(234, 1, '2015-09-21 10:44:51', '2015-09-21 10:44:51', '<h1 id="section-title">About Us</h1>\n<h3>Who We Are</h3>\nTimeous offers a wide range of events and entertainment services, an innovative company specializing planning, designing and managing all event types. We have established a strong business network while representing a diverse roster of clients. Whatever your requirements maybe, and however spectacular your concepts are, we turn them into reality. We understand the impact and importance of events, and envision providing you with distinctive ideas, without losing the sight of your vision, deadline or even budget.\n<h3>What We Do</h3>\nAre you looking to entertain a hard to impress audience? Our creative team can provide time tested proven insight and out-of-the-box solutions that consistently exceed your expectations. At Timeous, we let your imagination guide us, and provide state of the art planning and workmanship enabling us to create your event beyond perfection.\n\nUtilize our experienced event team to help oversee your next event. Every event is an original master piece, designed to meet and satisfy your toughest requirements. We work with all event types from product launches to weddings to corporates, awards, or gala funds. We can take control of the full process from preparations, execution and wrap up.\n\nWhy Us\n\nOur clients benefit from the company’s depth of resources and its unparalleled expertise, leadership, \n\nand creative problem-solving. Our goal is to maximize our client’s growth potential by providing \n\nspecialized services to expand their brand. We introduce entertainment properties and provide our \n\nclients the opportunity to reduce their to-do list by enlisting us to handle our areas of expertise. Our \n\nmission is to give each client a unique experience through the entire project cycle.\n\nWe are industry professionals with a reputation for unique consultative approach, warm personalized \n\nservice and, above all, the execution of creative ideas. At Timeous, we understand the intricacies of \n\nevent planning and look forward to working closely with you to make your special event a success.\n\nBut enough about us—our services are all about you!', 'Events and entertainment', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '53-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 10:44:51', '2015-09-21 10:44:51', '', 53, 'http://52.5.189.130/index.php/2015/09/21/53-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
