(240, 1, '2015-09-21 10:57:58', '2015-09-21 10:57:58', 'Corporate events have to be perfect…no more, no less. Your guests expect it, you expect it, and most important of all—the boss expects it! Attendees pay attention to every single aspect of events. To make your special event or function truly memorable and exciting requires genuine flair, creativity and professionalism.\r\n\r\nThemes can also be instrumental in conveying complex information during presentations, conferences and training and development programs. The right theme will set the tone for corporate events and drive decisions about venues, menu selections, messaging, graphics, music and entertainment. It can turn a plain room into a place from another world through creative designs and concepts makes the event compelling.', 'Corporate Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'corporate-events', '', '', '2015-09-22 07:07:51', '2015-09-22 07:07:51', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_event&#038;p=240', 0, 'cpt_event', '', 0),
