(242, 1, '2015-09-21 11:09:46', '2015-09-21 11:09:46', 'Lifestyle events are an important part of life, and each lifestyle calls for unique events to be planned. Your premium and high profile parties, fashion shows, brunches etc., come within this category. For the elite of taste and mind breathe life in designing spectacular events and transforming it into a lifestyle.\r\n\r\nUnique, once-in-a-lifetime memories that are beyond imagination combined with branded touches with industry trends to elevate lifestyle events. Engage your crowd through the creative design and production of a meticulously orchestrated event. It’s for the people living life to its fullest, embroidered with style, stories, and vision.\r\n', 'Lifestyle Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lifestyle-events', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:10:00', '2015-09-21 11:10:00', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_event&#038;p=242', 0, 'cpt_event', '', 0),
