(244, 1, '2015-09-21 11:13:19', '2015-09-21 11:13:19', 'Each event is unique, with its own objectives and challenges. To plan a successful event, you need to know the objectives of your event and its target attendance so that you can design it and deliver an event to achieve your goals and secondly, developing a realistic and attainable budget.\r\n\r\nConferences connect people, breed innovation, build communities, and spark change.  A properly executed event can be leveraged to support an organization’s strategic vision. Success of any event depends upon the management of it. Proper and detailed management is not only the key, but also goes a long way to result into resounding success.', 'Conference and Ceremony Management', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'conference-and-ceremony-management', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:14:26', '2015-09-21 11:14:26', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_event&#038;p=244', 0, 'cpt_event', '', 0),
