(246, 1, '2015-09-21 11:16:21', '2015-09-21 11:16:21', 'With an event planning designed to propel your audience’s enthusiasm into outer space, you can launch your brand like a rocket. Timing plays an important role in connecting consumers at the right time, and the right place brings the necessary strength to the message communicated so that the consumer becomes a motivated user and fan of the brand.\r\n\r\nProduct launches and brand activations are about giving your clients the ideas and the platform that is needed to showcase their products, in order to propel them into the market in an effective manner and offer a consistent brand experience to your consumers that their captures the imagination.', 'Product Launches & Brand Activations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'product-launches-brand-activations', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:16:33', '2015-09-21 11:16:33', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_event&#038;p=246', 0, 'cpt_event', '', 0),
