(250, 1, '2015-09-21 11:20:37', '2015-09-21 11:20:37', 'Special Events is all about business. But sometimes, business is all about celebration. Coordinating the many details of special event planning can be a daunting task; there are a lot of details that go into planning a successful event.\r\n\r\nCreate an event design personally tailored to the personality and look and turn concepts for life''s celebrations into a reality. Accomplish all the details that you have envisioned and more importantly enjoy the pleasure of truly enjoying the journey to a memorable celebration with the guarantee of a flawless execution.', 'Special Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'special-events', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:20:37', '2015-09-21 11:20:37', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_event&#038;p=250', 0, 'cpt_event', '', 0),
