(252, 1, '2015-09-21 11:21:51', '2015-09-21 11:21:51', 'The design, realization and coordination of a successful exhibition presence is a complex task. Planning your participation at an exhibition is about knowing what you want to achieve.\r\n\r\nIt''s not enough to exhibit because the exhibition organizer tells you your competitors are there or because your sales team believes you should exhibit. Promoting your business at exhibitions can be a rewarding experience. Select the exhibition because it fulfills your exhibiting objectives and your expectations are realized and your event is successful.', 'Exhibition Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'exhibition-services', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:21:51', '2015-09-21 11:21:51', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_event&#038;p=252', 0, 'cpt_event', '', 0),
