(257, 1, '2015-09-21 11:42:12', '2015-09-21 11:42:12', 'While you are working on making more great music, an artist manager is contacting people on your behalf who can help advance your career and create new opportunities. When the music is ready, the artist manager provides the introductions to important people in the music business, to producers and studios.\r\n\r\nA manager is primarily interested in the commercial viability of your creative work; ensure that your music and performance receives a high level of exposure to the audience feel they need to reach. We are the artist management team to take your career to the next level so you can continue to make great music.', 'Artist Management', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'artist-management', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:47:29', '2015-09-21 11:47:29', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_discography&#038;p=257', 0, 'cpt_discography', '', 0),
