(265, 1, '2015-09-21 11:55:07', '2015-09-21 11:55:07', 'It is true that everyone loves gifts! And, ceremonies are such occasion where people are showered with them. Be it their relatives, friends or colleagues, everybody gets lovely presents. Finding the right return gifts for ceremonies can be quite a daunting task for most, many of those running short on return gift ideas have turned to the internet to provide them with a way out.\r\n\r\nSo, why not reciprocate their gesture by giving them a return gift? It will not only make them happy, but will also make them feel special and honored. It is just a way of saying ''thank you'' to your guests.', 'Return Gifts', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'return-gifts', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:55:07', '2015-09-21 11:55:07', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_discography&#038;p=265', 0, 'cpt_discography', '', 0),
