(267, 1, '2015-09-21 11:56:37', '2015-09-21 11:56:37', 'Back in the day, wedding receptions were clean and contained four-hours long. Now, that''s no longer the case. While the bride and groom used to exit before the guests, they now choose to stay and party all night long.\r\n\r\nSometimes brides and grooms would prefer to stay somewhere private, where their guests aren''t, that night and its upto them to find a hotel where the guests won''t be staying. If you know that guests want to stay at this particular hotel because of its location, etc., then it becomes your responsibility to find another place to stay for the privacy.', 'Staying of bride and groom', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'staying-of-bride-and-groom', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:56:37', '2015-09-21 11:56:37', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_discography&#038;p=267', 0, 'cpt_discography', '', 0),
