(272, 1, '2015-09-21 11:59:36', '2015-09-21 11:59:36', 'The work of a logistician begins with bringing in the supplies and raw materials necessary for a business or organization to operate. The job of a logistician is to make sure goods and services get into the hands of consumers.\r\n\r\nAs the global economy has expanded, logistics has become increasingly important. Without the planning and execution of the distribution of resources, society as we know it would cease to function.', 'Logistic management', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'logistic-management', '', '', '2015-09-21 11:59:36', '2015-09-21 11:59:36', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_discography&#038;p=272', 0, 'cpt_discography', '', 0),
