(274, 1, '2015-09-21 12:01:07', '2015-09-21 12:01:07', 'Lighting can be extremely important for your event. Depending on your affair, lighting can set the mood of your theme and motivate guests to dance. There are different types of lighting that can make this magical color spectacle happen.\r\n\r\nIntelligent lighting is a term used for an innovative type of party or stage light. Their automated mechanism allows the lights to move and create complicated and colorful effects. For celebrations, intelligent lighting can create lighting arrangements of your desired color to match your theme. If you want to create an elegant ambiance for your event or if you are looking for a ways to impress your guests and set the mood for dancing, then using intelligent lighting is your solution.', 'Intelligent lighting and Ambiance', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'intelligent-lighting-and-ambiance', '', '', '2015-09-21 12:01:07', '2015-09-21 12:01:07', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?post_type=cpt_discography&#038;p=274', 0, 'cpt_discography', '', 0),
