(282, 1, '2015-09-21 13:39:49', '2015-09-21 13:39:49', 'When it comes to planning the big day, there''s nothing so hard as choosing the wedding venue. It’s expensive. It sets the tone. There are so many things to consider, cost being the biggest. When all is said and done, your venue (including your ceremony and reception) will be the largest budgetary item on your wedding planning list. We also believe that because of this, selecting your venue can also be one of the most challenging and stressful.\r\n\r\nIt is important to align the vision and plan that you have for your wedding day with your wedding venue in order to determine how your chosen venue can suit your needs. You are about to undertake an incredible journey, the efforts of which will only be brought to fruition on your wedding day!', 'Venue Selection', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'venue-selection', '', '', '2015-09-21 13:39:49', '2015-09-21 13:39:49', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?page_id=282', 0, 'page', '', 0),
