(285, 1, '2015-09-21 13:42:38', '2015-09-21 13:42:38', 'Your wedding invitations give guests a glimpse at your wedding theme will set the tone for your whole day, so you need to make sure you get it right.\r\n\r\nChoosing your invitations and other printed matter is often the first taste of all the creative wedding planning to come. You’ve entered a world filled with rich colors, regal monograms and shimmering papers—and wide-ranging costs. There are numerous parts of an invitation. Beside the invite, you may also find an ensemble of various cards that are for the different occasions to be held on different days.\r\n\r\nThe best advice to avoid stress is to start looking for your invitations early. This will allow you ample time to consider all of your choices which complements your situation, style, and spirit of your wedding and ensure that your wedding invitations are as unique and as special as your big day.', 'Wedding cards', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wedding-cards', '', '', '2015-09-21 13:42:38', '2015-09-21 13:42:38', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?page_id=285', 0, 'page', '', 0),
