(288, 1, '2015-09-21 13:45:29', '2015-09-21 13:45:29', 'Arranging accommodation for you and your guests on top of a wedding can be another source of stress. Weddings should always be all about the happy couple. It is one of the most important days of your life. For wedding guests, it is a time to celebrate with the newlywed couple, and attending the wedding is their contribution to the event.\r\n\r\nIt is therefore important where necessary to find the right accommodation for your wedding guests, most especially if there are some of them who come from faraway places. It’s your big day: a very special occasion and one which you will want to remember (and will want your guests to remember) for many years to come.', 'Accommodations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accommodations', '', '', '2015-09-21 13:45:29', '2015-09-21 13:45:29', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?page_id=288', 0, 'page', '', 0),
