(291, 1, '2015-09-21 13:52:03', '2015-09-21 13:52:03', 'Getting your wedding decoration sorted is not an easy task. It''s not just a case of hanging up some bunting and putting candles in jars - you''ll want your wedding guests to be wowed by your choice of color, theme and attention to detail.\r\n\r\nWedding decor is a really individual aspect to the day and should reflect your taste and style perfectly. You want ensure it''s the magical, memorable, and altogether perfect day you envision and plan a wedding that exceeds your dreams but not your budget. When the big day comes your venue will be dressed perfectly so you won’t have to worry about a thing and can simply enjoy your special day!', 'Décor and Ambience', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'decor-and-ambience', '', '', '2015-09-21 13:52:03', '2015-09-21 13:52:03', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?page_id=291', 0, 'page', '', 0);
