(297, 1, '2015-09-21 13:56:01', '2015-09-21 13:56:01', 'Every wedding guest secretly hopes for amazing food and what you feed your guests will be noted and noticed.  When you are planning your wedding, you want to keep it simple, elegant, and most importantly under budget because every decision you make impacts the cost.\r\n\r\nYour wedding food is important not only for photos, but for taste because your food and drinks not only fuel the party (literally), they also add personality and style to your wedding. Choosing the right caterer is very important. The catering expert will be able to help you choose the proper menu and assist you in giving ideas for decorations to create a memorable event that meets your goals and budgets.', 'Food & Beverage Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'food-beverage-services', '', '', '2015-09-21 13:56:01', '2015-09-21 13:56:01', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?page_id=297', 0, 'page', '', 0),
