(300, 1, '2015-09-21 13:57:29', '2015-09-21 13:57:29', 'After the wedding day, those photos and video are all that''s left to help you remember the day. Your pictures will not only bring back memories but also the emotions that you experienced during one of the most important day of your life. You are going to be able to relive the emotions, the joy, the tears, the words, the colors and sounds that made your wedding day a day to cherish forever.\r\n\r\nIt is more than point and shoot; it is a living, moving memory with sights and sounds, it is a keepsake to be passed down to kids (and grandkids!) Your photos will be beautiful, clear, sharp, and full of emotion, capturing your story. The first moment as a husband and wife will be a moment frozen in time.', 'Photography and Videography', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'photography-and-videography', '', '', '2015-09-21 13:57:29', '2015-09-21 13:57:29', '', 0, 'http://52.5.189.130/?page_id=300', 0, 'page', '', 0),
