(312, 1, '2015-09-21 14:15:13', '2015-09-21 14:15:13', 'It is a highly competitive industry, where having talent is just not enough; you need the people to help you. Whether you are new or a seasoned professional, if acting or being a performer is your passion you want to create a connection between the best and most promising people, on the one side, and the producers with the just the right roles for them, on the other side.\r\n\r\nIn the entertainment industry, it is advisable to create professional portfolio because portfolio act as an important marketing tool for a model or an actor and increases your chances to get that contract you have been dreaming about. It provides you with a competitive edge in a cut throat industry, and helps you highlights your strength and experience.\r\n\r\nYou need people that will invest in you for your portfolio and always on advice you what is best for you. An Agency will promote you its entire local and international sector it represents, without you having the hassle of sending your profile everywhere.\r\n\r\nWe help you in following services\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Movies</li>\r\n	<li>Serial daily episodes</li>\r\n	<li>Ads films</li>\r\n	<li>Commercials</li>\r\n	<li>International shoots</li>\r\n	<li>Creative portfolio with best photographer''s team outdoor and indoor with different concepts</li>\r\n</ul>', 'PortFolio and Casting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '277-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 14:15:13', '2015-09-21 14:15:13', '', 277, 'http://52.5.189.130/index.php/2015/09/21/277-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
